      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "ZIPPING GRESSIER (2) was a last start winner (30.09) from Box 8 at this track. Can continue on his winning ways. STOCK'S GIFT (1) had a tricky draw last time and although midfield in fifth wasn't far away finishing 4.5 lengths from the winner (23.26). Has a good record here at this journey. Should be thereabouts. SAVINA (8) filled a minor placing last start at this track behind Dollar Rolex (23.12) in a Grade 5. Led around the bend before fighting on well and should give a sight. Safe beginner but wide box to overcome and will need some luck. Can feature again. PRINCE VINNIE (5) has top-three claims while fresh from a seven weeks break.",
